parameters:
\F[nako_angry]Nadeshiko: "No, no more! Akane... to lock me up like
this...!"

\F[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "Did Akane take me somewhere...? But then... that
means Akane is in danger..."

\F[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "Akane alone has no chance against the swim
team..."

\F[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "And yet she went to save me... always rushing
off like that... Akane..."

Akane: "Nyyururru~♪ Nadeshiko... I won't let you escape
now♪"
